StructureDefinition-CareConnect-ProcedureRequest-1

Procedure Request

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

The following elements are mandatory in the FHIR profile (i.e. MUST be present):

  1. status
  2. intent
  3. code
  4. subject
  5. performer

Examples

  • CareConnect-ProcedureRequest-1 Example
